title: What happened to Twisted Treeline Co-op vs AI?
body: I remember logging on sometime either 2013 or 2014 and going into the Co-op vs AI section and seeing Twisted Treeline as an option and playing on it, here on the OCE server. What happened to that? Is that ever coming back to OCE?

replies.body:
***CLAP CLAP CLAP CLAP CLAP***

They programmed bots for TT?
